nodes.text: Antiques dealers were individuals who sold antiques for a living. The human male Antron Bach worked as an antiques dealer before being asked to guard a horde of Jedi treasures by the Jedi Order following Order 66. The Ithorian collector Dok-Ondar was a antiques dealer who ran a Den of Antiquities in Black Spire Outpost on the planet Batuu.
An antiques dealer first appeared in the short story "The End of History", which was written by Alexander Freed and published in Star Wars Insider 154 in 2014.
